        .process__step 03
        h3.process__card-title Build & Collaborate

      .process__card-divider

      .process__card-body
        .process__card-label Development
        .process__card-content
          p.process__card-description I bridge design and development — working with HTML, CSS, JS, and modern tools to ensure pixel-perfect and performant execution.
          .process__card-tags
            span.process__tag HTML
            span.process__tag CSS
            span.process__tag JavaScript
            span.process__tag PUG
            span.process__tag SASS
            span.process__tag GSAP
            span.process__tag Framer
            span.process__tag Webflow

    .process__card(data-step="04")
      .process__card-header
        .process__step 04
        h3.process__card-title Optimize & Scale

      .process__card-divider

      .process__card-body
        .process__card-label Growth
        .process__card-content
          p.process__card-description I iterate based on feedback, optimize performance, and ensure the product scales effectively across users and platforms.
          .process__card-tags
            span.process__tag Testing
            span.process__tag Performance Optimization
            span.process__tag Iteration

    .process__card(data-step="05")
      .process__card-header
        .process__step 05
        h3.process__card-title Designing with AI

      .process__card-divider

      .process__card-body
        .process__card-label AI
        .process__card-content
          p.process__card-description I leverage AI tools to accelerate ideation, improve workflows, and build faster without compromising quality.
